data.description: This Margate home is located to close proximity to the Seminole Hard Rock casino of Coconut Creek, great restaurants, shops, hospitals, Margate water park, major roads and highways.    The home boast a huge backyard (13,183 square feet) with plenty of room for a pool and all your toys like a boat or RV. Also on the backyard is a real tree two floors tree house for the entertainment of children and adults alike, and included is a dock on the canal on the back of the home.    In the inside this home has tile floors through out the living areas and wood floors in the bedrooms, the kitchen has been updated with granite counter tops and it overlooks the yard and water, it also has plenty of cabinets. Other features include a 4th bedroom with AC and a laundry room.
